data.description: Nice country setting with a great view!!! Four bedroom, 2 1/5 bath home on a nicely treed 1.15 acre lot. Over 2,700 square feet of living space. Newer windows throughout, 5 year old furnace and a new 75 gallon hot water heater. Spacious oak kitchen with tons of cabinets and a breakfast bar area. Large formal dining room and an extra large living room with sliding doors leading to the covered porch. Main floor laundry with half bath. There is one bedroom and a full bath on the main floor for those in need of a main floor master. The second floor has 3 bedrooms, a full bath and a 15 x 15 area at the top of the stairs that would make a great home office, workout room, craft room or a place for the kids to hang out. All the bedrooms have closet organizers in the ample sized closets. This home has a wide wrap around porch and the back of the home has decking and a custom paver patio with a pergola covering. There is also a small pond off the patio area.. Ok, now for the part the guys will like. There is an extra large 2 car garage with a walk up finished 2nd level with heat, a kitchenette and a bathroom. This would make the ultimate man cave, an office away from the main house or a place for your older kid to stay. There is also a half bath on the main level of the garage. The property also has a woodshop building with 100 amp service and a cement floor. City water and septic. Make an appointment before this awesome property is gone.
